description: Charming 350 sq ft Chelsea Studio to sublet from Feb 4 to Mar 4 (full month discount). Located on lovely tree-lined W22nd St between 9th & 10th avenues, apt is on the ground floor rear of a brownstone overlooking garden (very quiet). Fully furnished. WASHER/DRYER IN APARTMENT.  Computer available with high speed wired internet & WiFi. 32" TV with HBO/Amazon/Netflix. This is a great deal to be in the heart of a popular and very safe neighborhood, steps away from the Highline and Gallery District.
name: Charming Chelsea Studio
